this is a misunderstanding.

255
00:12:47,166 --> 00:12:49,041
This is just a keepsake
from a friend.

256
00:12:49,125 --> 00:12:50,458
[gasps]

257
00:12:50,541 --> 00:12:51,875
[MAN]
I'll hear no more!

258
00:12:51,958 --> 00:12:53,666
I will avenge
my fallen brethren,

259
00:12:53,750 --> 00:12:55,333
even if it means
taking your head.

260
00:12:55,416 --> 00:12:58,375
Today you will die,
evil pig leader!

261
00:12:58,458 --> 00:13:00,416
[RANGA]
What should we do?

262
00:13:00,500 --> 00:13:01,666
[RIMURU]
Good question.

263
00:13:02,958 --> 00:13:05,250
You take care
of the pink-haired one.

264
00:13:05,333 --> 00:13:06,541
[RANGA]
Yes, master.

265
00:13:06,625 --> 00:13:08,708
-[RIMURU] Do not kill her.
-[RANGA] Sir?

266
00:13:09,750 --> 00:13:11,583
[RIMURU] I think
there's more to all this.

267
00:13:11,666 --> 00:13:13,625
So just run interference for me.

268
00:13:13,708 --> 00:13:15,333
I'll take care of the rest.

269
00:13:15,416 --> 00:13:19,916
[RANGA] But that would leave you
to fight five ogres by yourself.

270
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:23,166
[RIMURU] It'll be fine.
I don't plan on losing.

271
00:13:23,250 --> 00:13:26,333
[RANGA] As expected
of my master. Leave it to me.

272
00:13:26,416 --> 00:13:29,083
You underestimate us.

273
00:13:29,166 --> 00:13:32,208
You are very brave,
or very stupid.

274
00:13:32,291 --> 00:13:34,250
Regardless,
I'm happy to face you.

275
00:13:34,333 --> 00:13:37,416
It should be a decent fight,
as well as your last!

276
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:39,250
[grunting]

277
00:13:43,666 --> 00:13:46,708
[gasping]

278
00:13:46,791 --> 00:13:48,416
[grunting]

279
00:13:48,500 --> 00:13:50,083
[RIMURU]
Looks like you need a nap.

280
00:13:51,250 --> 00:13:53,833
[groaning]

281
00:13:53,916 --> 00:13:56,416
♪

282
00:13:56,500 --> 00:13:57,750
[groans weakly]

283
00:13:59,083 --> 00:14:01,541
[RIMURU] Sorry, but I saw you
coming with Magic Sense.

284
00:14:01,625 --> 00:14:03,541
Holy hooters!

285
00:14:03,625 --> 00:14:06,666
Wait, I swear that's not what
I meant when I said I saw you.

286
00:14:08,291 --> 00:14:09,291
[gasps]

287
00:14:09,375 --> 00:14:10,333
[grunts]

288
00:14:12,291 --> 00:14:14,541
[RIMURU] I've never had a woman
fall so hard for me.

289
00:14:14,625 --> 00:14:16,041
Just kidding.

290
00:14:16,125 --> 00:14:17,500
♪

291
00:14:17,583 --> 00:14:18,458
[clang]

292
00:14:25,250 --> 00:14:26,833
[groaning]

293
00:14:29,250 --> 00:14:31,333
-Whoa!
-Way to go, sir!

294
00:14:31,416 --> 00:14:32,500
[RANGA growling]

295
00:14:32,583 --> 00:14:33,833
[WOMAN]
He beat us that easily?

296
00:14:33,916 --> 00:14:36,000
[RIMURU]
That's three down.

297
00:14:36,083 --> 00:14:38,250
All right, who's next?

298
00:14:38,333 --> 00:14:39,958
[OLD MAN]
Hmm.

299
00:14:41,041 --> 00:14:43,625
The Centipede's
Paralysis Breath.

300
00:14:43,708 --> 00:14:46,458
The Black Spider's
Sticky Steel Thread.

301
00:14:46,541 --> 00:14:48,541
And the Armorsaurus' Body Armor.

302
00:14:48,625 --> 00:14:50,000
[RIMURU gasps]

303
00:14:50,083 --> 00:14:52,000
[OLD MAN] There's no telling
just how many skills

304
00:14:52,083 --> 00:14:54,166
he may possess
from other monsters.

305
00:14:54,250 --> 00:14:56,625
Do not let your guard down,
young master.

306
00:14:57,791 --> 00:14:59,833
[RIMURU] That old guy was able
to name off my skills

307
00:14:59,916 --> 00:15:02,708
and the monsters they came
from with one quick look?

308
00:15:02,791 --> 00:15:05,958
I might need to play my cards
a little closer to my chest.

309
00:15:07,166 --> 00:15:09,000
Can we stop this, already?

310
00:15:09,083 --> 00:15:11,333
I'd still be interested
in talking things out.

311
00:15:11,416 --> 00:15:14,125
Quiet! Enough, majin.

312
00:15:14,208 --> 00:15:16,375
[RIMURU]
So, uh, is that a no?

313
00:15:16,458 --> 00:15:18,791
I admit you're rather strong,

314
00:15:18,875 --> 00:15:20,791
which only confirms
my suspicions.

315
00:15:20,875 --> 00:15:21,958
[RIMURU]
Which is what?

316
00:15:22,041 --> 00:15:24,416
That you are
obviously one of them.

317
00:15:24,500 --> 00:15:26,416
Who's "them"?

318
00:15:27,416 --> 00:15:29,541
[MAN] It is unthinkable
that we mighty ogres

319
00:15:29,625 --> 00:15:31,833
would be defeated
by a bunch of lowly orcs.

320
00:15:31,916 --> 00:15:34,958
[RIMURU] Orcs? Whoa, can we just
back up for a second?

321
00:15:35,041 --> 00:15:36,541
Silence!

322
00:15:36,625 --> 00:15:39,083
I know it was you and the work
of your majin comrades.

323
00:15:39,166 --> 00:15:40,458
[RIMURU]
Uh, come again?

324
00:15:40,541 --> 00:15:41,875
It was you!

325
00:15:41,958 --> 00:15:43,666
[RIMURU] Listen, you've got
this all wrong.

326
00:15:43,750 --> 00:15:45,000
[gasps]

327
00:15:45,083 --> 00:15:46,500
Huh?

328
00:15:49,375 --> 00:15:53,125
[OLD MAN] Hmm. I must be
getting slow in my old age.

329
00:15:53,208 --> 00:15:55,500
I was certain
that I'd cut off your head.

330
00:15:55,583 --> 00:15:57,708
[RIMURU]
What the heck?

331
00:15:57,791 --> 00:15:59,083
Lord Rimuru!

332
00:15:59,166 --> 00:16:00,291
Uh-oh, your arm.

333
00:16:00,375 --> 00:16:02,291
[RANGA growling]
Master.

334
00:16:02,375 --> 00:16:03,916
[RIMURU]
I'm fine.

335
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,625
Don't let your guard down.

336
00:16:06,750 --> 00:16:08,791
He got past my Magic Sense

337
00:16:08,875 --> 00:16:11,791
and broke through my Multilayer
Barrier and Body Armor?

338
00:16:11,875 --> 00:16:14,833
[OLD MAN]
Next time, I won't miss.

339
00:16:14,916 --> 00:16:17,583
It would appear you're driven
by sheer foolishness.

340
00:16:17,666 --> 00:16:21,750
I must commend your ability to
remain calm after losing an arm.

341
00:16:24,416 --> 00:16:27,000
However, your arrogance
will be your downfall.

342
00:16:27,083 --> 00:16:29,625
I told you not to
underestimate us ogres.

343
00:16:29,708 --> 00:16:31,458
Perhaps you'll be smarter
in your next life!

344
00:16:31,541 --> 00:16:33,750
♪

345
00:16:43,791 --> 00:16:45,250
-[gasps]
-Huh?

346
00:16:45,333 --> 00:16:46,583
[RIMURU laughs]

347
00:16:46,666 --> 00:16:48,875
You think chopping off
an arm will stop me?

348
00:16:48,958 --> 00:16:50,625
Sheesh.
And you called me arrogant.

349
00:16:50,708 --> 00:16:52,000
[grunts]

350
00:16:52,083 --> 00:16:53,833
You will die here!

351
00:16:54,958 --> 00:16:56,875
Ogre Flame!

352
00:16:56,958 --> 00:16:58,916
♪

353
00:17:03,333 --> 00:17:07,125
-[OLD MAN] Young master.
-Is he dead?

354
00:17:07,208 --> 00:17:08,416
[gasps]

355
00:17:10,291 --> 00:17:11,333
[gasps]

356
00:17:13,125 --> 00:17:17,041
[RIMURU] What a shame.
Fire immunity, am I right?

357
00:17:17,125 --> 00:17:21,750
I do have to give you credit.
I underestimated your abilities.

358
00:17:23,083 --> 00:17:26,500
In return, I won't hold back.

359
00:17:27,666 --> 00:17:28,791
[grunts]

360
00:17:30,875 --> 00:17:32,833
[OLD MAN]
His aura's incredible.

361
00:17:34,125 --> 00:17:35,500
Take it all in, boys.

362
00:17:35,583 --> 00:17:37,833
♪

363
00:17:40,791 --> 00:17:42,083
[gasps]

364
00:17:47,791 --> 00:17:50,250
Huh? No way! That's impossible.

365
00:17:50,333 --> 00:17:52,416
Normally a magic flame
would be produced

366
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:54,333
by the surrounding magicules.

367
00:17:54,416 --> 00:17:55,625
But this flame is different,

368
00:17:55,708 --> 00:17:57,666
it's powered by nothing
but his strength.

369
00:17:59,208 --> 00:18:00,416
And the size of the flame

370
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:02,708
is reflecting the size
of his power.

371
00:18:03,916 --> 00:18:07,208
Don't worry, the show's
not over yet, folks.

372
00:18:07,291 --> 00:18:09,750
Because I'm just
getting started!

373
00:18:09,833 --> 00:18:11,125
[gasps]

374
00:18:14,625 --> 00:18:16,750
[groans]

375
00:18:16,833 --> 00:18:17,791
Huh?

376
00:18:17,875 --> 00:18:19,333
[electricity crackling]

377
00:18:20,458 --> 00:18:21,875
[RIMURU]
Oops.

378
00:18:21,958 --> 00:18:24,958
So much for keeping
my cards close to my chest, huh?

379
00:18:26,625 --> 00:18:28,291
What now? Still wanna fight?

380
00:18:28,375 --> 00:18:30,000
[grunts]

381
00:18:30,083 --> 00:18:31,791
[RIMURU]
Good, he seems scared.

382
00:18:31,875 --> 00:18:33,916
Come on, man,
just surrender already.

383
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:36,750
[OLD MAN] Sir, Please take
the princess and flee.

384
00:18:36,833 --> 00:18:37,875
I shall end this.

385
00:18:37,958 --> 00:18:40,000
Quiet, old man.

386
00:18:40,083 --> 00:18:41,250
[OLD MAN sighs]

387
00:18:42,708 --> 00:18:44,625
That's an intense flame.

388
00:18:44,708 --> 00:18:46,083
I hate to admit it,

389
00:18:46,166 --> 00:18:48,458
but it would appear
that we're no match for you.

390
00:18:49,666 --> 00:18:52,625
That doesn't matter.
I refuse to run away.

391
00:18:52,708 --> 00:18:56,166
As the leader of the powerful
ogre clan, I must stand proud.

392
00:18:56,250 --> 00:18:59,083
I cannot leave until
I've avenged my slain brethren.

393
00:18:59,166 --> 00:19:00,791
I must defeat you!

394
00:19:02,125 --> 00:19:05,208
Even if I die,
I will fight to my last breath.

395
00:19:05,291 --> 00:19:07,583
[OLD MAN] Young master,
it would be an old man's honor

396
00:19:07,666 --> 00:19:09,041
to fight alongside you.

397
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:12,375
[RIMURU]
Seriously? Well, damn.

398
00:19:12,458 --> 00:19:14,750
This bluff totally backfired.

399
00:19:14,833 --> 00:19:16,583
[panting]

400
00:19:16,666 --> 00:19:18,833
Brother, stop, I beg of you!

401
00:19:18,916 --> 00:19:21,083
This man,
he may not be our enemy.

402
00:19:21,166 --> 00:19:22,583
Out of my way!

403
00:19:22,666 --> 00:19:24,666
-No!
-[gasps]

404
00:19:24,750 --> 00:19:27,708
Why? He's a masked majin,
is he not?

405
00:19:27,791 --> 00:19:30,250
He's just like the one
who attacked our village.

406
00:19:30,333 --> 00:19:31,666
You saw the mask yourself.

407
00:19:31,750 --> 00:19:34,291
Yes, but please,

408
00:19:34,375 --> 00:19:36,916
we need to try
and think about this calmly.

409
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:39,291
It's true
that he's extremely powerful.

410
00:19:39,375 --> 00:19:41,166
So why would he hire orcs?

411
00:19:41,250 --> 00:19:43,541
Why use them to
indirectly attack our village?

412
00:19:43,625 --> 00:19:44,666
It makes no sense.

413
00:19:44,750 --> 00:19:47,125
Obviously, he's strong enough

414
00:19:47,208 --> 00:19:49,250
to kill us by himself
if he wanted to.

415
00:19:49,333 --> 00:19:50,833
Mm-hmm.

416
00:19:50,916 --> 00:19:52,916
[WOMAN] There is no doubt
that he is different from us.

417
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:55,541
And he's strong,
but I truly believe

418
00:19:55,625 --> 00:19:57,666
that he has no connection
to the attack.

419
00:19:57,750 --> 00:19:59,250
[softly]
Huh? Hmm?

420
00:20:02,333 --> 00:20:04,916
How about it, are you
more willing to talk now?

421
00:20:06,041 --> 00:20:07,500
I'll just put this away.

422
00:20:12,625 --> 00:20:14,125
Tell us who you are.

423
00:20:14,208 --> 00:20:15,458
Really.

424
00:20:15,541 --> 00:20:18,791
Me? I'm just a friendly slime.

425
00:20:18,875 --> 00:20:20,750
Seriously?

426
00:20:20,833 --> 00:20:23,291
Yeah. Rimuru the Slime.

427
00:20:24,958 --> 00:20:26,125
[BOTH gasp]

428
00:20:29,916 --> 00:20:31,666
So it's true, then.

429
00:20:33,458 --> 00:20:36,416
[RIMURU] As I said, this mask
is a keepsake from a friend.

430
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:38,583
You're welcome to look at it
and see if it's the same one

431
00:20:38,666 --> 00:20:41,125
the person who attacked
your village used.

432
00:20:42,833 --> 00:20:44,125
Very well.

433
00:20:45,875 --> 00:20:47,750
It does seem similar, but...

434
00:20:48,875 --> 00:20:52,166
[WOMAN] This one has some kind
of magic suppression power.

435
00:20:52,250 --> 00:20:54,166
[OLD MAN]
The majin who attacked back then

436
00:20:54,250 --> 00:20:57,666
wasn't doing anything
to conceal their aura.

437
00:20:57,750 --> 00:20:58,916
So then...

438
00:21:00,583 --> 00:21:02,291
forgive us.

439
00:21:02,375 --> 00:21:06,458
We were too quick to judge
and behaved rashly.

440
00:21:06,541 --> 00:21:08,750
Please accept my apology.

441
00:21:08,833 --> 00:21:10,541
[RIMURU]
Sure, it's all good.

442
00:21:10,625 --> 00:21:12,791
Yowza!

443
00:21:12,875 --> 00:21:15,625
For a minute there, things
were lookin' pretty hairy.

444
00:21:16,791 --> 00:21:19,291
Well, we should probably
talk somewhere else.

445
00:21:19,375 --> 00:21:22,291
Let's go back to our village.
You can join us there.

446
00:21:22,375 --> 00:21:24,250
Wait. Are you sure?

447
00:21:24,333 --> 00:21:27,333
[RIMURU] Yep. I'd like to hear
what happened to you.

448
00:21:29,208 --> 00:21:31,666
But we attacked you
and wounded your companions.

449
00:21:31,750 --> 00:21:34,166
And we put the hurt
on some of yours.

450
00:21:34,250 --> 00:21:37,166
But, hey, no one kicked
the bucket, so we're cool.

451
00:21:37,250 --> 00:21:40,166
-I'm sorry I injured you.
-[GOBTA gasping]

452
00:21:40,250 --> 00:21:41,666
[RIGUR chuckles]

453
00:21:41,750 --> 00:21:43,791
[RIMURU] Besides, we're having
a huge feast today.

454
00:21:43,875 --> 00:21:45,791
More people just means more fun.

455
00:21:45,875 --> 00:21:48,083
-[gasps]
-[chuckles]

456
00:21:49,750 --> 00:21:51,625
[RIMURU] And so,
the battle which had begun

457
00:21:51,708 --> 00:21:54,291
before we even knew why ended.

458
00:21:54,375 --> 00:21:57,458
The ogre princess agreed
to reverse the sleep spell,

459
00:21:57,541 --> 00:21:59,791
and all the goblins
and wolves woke up.

460
00:21:59,875 --> 00:22:02,791
Rimuru healed everybody's wounds
with his potions,

461
00:22:02,875 --> 00:22:05,208
and then the whole gang headed
back to the goblin village

462
00:22:05,291 --> 00:22:08,208
to prepare for the big feast.

463
00:22:08,291 --> 00:22:09,833
So, hey, what's your name?

464
00:22:09,916 --> 00:22:13,291
Oh, I'm afraid
we do not possess names.

465
00:22:13,375 --> 00:22:17,416
Of course. I forgot
that's a thing around here.

466
00:22:17,500 --> 00:22:20,250
That's right. That's right.

467
00:23:53,291 --> 00:23:55,916
[GREAT SAGE]
Next time, "The Orc Lord."

